title: Cisco Catalyst 9000: Stack Ring Redundancy
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Checks whether the StackWise stack ports of a Cisco Catalyst 9000 series
 switch form a redundant ring. The state is read from the
 CISCO-STACKWISE-MIB (cswRingRedundant).

 The check is OK when the stack ports form a redundant ring and CRITICAL
 when they do not.

inventory:
 One service is created per host.
